  "body": "# Rationale\r\n\r\nWhile testing the merge in the Ropsten testnet, I tried to add current block _difficulty_ to my dashboards and realized this is not exposed. Such metric can be used to improve monitoring with tools like Prometheus and Alertmanager, alarms can be triggered upon thresholds set by the node operator and get notified.\r\n\r\nBonus if _totalDifficulty_ could also be exposed, since the monitoring tools can compare with _difficulty_.",
